    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个分组逻辑。每个任务持续时间等于它标注的数字，比如8s任务就持续8秒，而且任务之间要串行执行，后一个等前一个完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "8s",
        "7s",
        "6s",
        "after",
        "sequential"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先设置时间格式。dateFormat用SS表示秒，axisFormat用%S显示秒数。然后建三个section，ID=0里面8s从00开始，7s接在8s后面，6s接在7s后面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat SS",
        "axisFormat %S",
        "8s, 00, 8s",
        "7s, after 8s, 7s",
        "6s, after 7s, 6s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ID=1和ID=2也是同样的串行结构吧？5s从00开始，然后4s、3s依次后接；ID=2的2s从00开始，1s接在后面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section ID=1",
        "5s, 00, 5s",
        "4s, after 5s, 4s",
        "3s, after 4s, 3s",
        "section ID=2",
        "2s, 00, 2s",
        "1s, after 2s, 1s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个section的任务都是各自独立的流水线，都从00时刻启动第一条任务。我检查一下：ID=0是8s→7s→6s，ID=1是5s→4s→3s，ID=2是2s→1s，全部用after关键字串联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "after 8s",
        "after 7s",
        "after 5s",
        "after 4s",
        "after 2s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——ID=2只有2s和1s两个任务，不是三个。你确认下数量对不对。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section ID=2",
